  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Content Model</h2>

    <h3>Permitted Content</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Flow content, but no <code>&lt;header&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code>, sectioning, or heading elements</li>
      <li>Inline elements: <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;code&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;em&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;strong&gt;</code>, etc.</li>
      <li>Text content</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Required Parent</h3>
    <p>Must be a child of <code>&lt;dl&gt;</code>, optionally wrapped in a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>.</p>

    <h3>Required Siblings</h3>
    <p>Must be followed by one or more <code>&lt;dd&gt;</code> elements (or preceded by <code>&lt;dt&gt;</code> elements that share the same <code>&lt;dd&gt;</code>).</p>
  </section>

